Difference between Advanced and "beginner":
Advanced is designed for professionals who design their databases.  It has features like script debugging, variable monitoring, database analysis tools, etc.  

Designing a database can be as powerful as designing a program in a language, but learning is easier, especially with the tools.  But it can also involve the same debugging issues.

Regular Filemaker Pro can design files but without the tools.  It is usually purchased for users who use databases designed by professionals.  Cheaper.
